1. variables can be defined in the inventory file or playbook or others
2. variables type = string, boolean, number, list, dictionary
3. "{{ var_name }}" 



1. sudo apt update => download information about packages and their versions
2. sudo apt upgrade <packagename> => upgrade the package to latest version
4. sudo apt install <packagename> => install a package
5. sudo apt remove <packagename> => remove a packageubuntu.sources
6. sudo apt search <packagename> => search for a package 
7. sudo dpkg -i <debian file> => to install a package
8. sudo dpkg -r <packagename> => to remove a package



system modules, file modules, command module
